<span id="freeTextContainer2333187950174106286">When I see the news reporting tragedy, I pray for more love &amp; laughter all around. <br/><br/>&quot;The world is violent and mercurial - it will have its way with you. We are saved only by love - love for each other and the love that we pour into the art we feel compelled to share: being a parent; being a writer; being a painter; being a friend. We live in a perpetually burning building, and what we must save from it, all the time, is love.&quot; </span>
